import React from "react";
import ReactDOM from "react-dom";
import App3 from './App3';
import './index.css'
import { BrowserRouter } from "react-router-dom";
import CryptoContext from "./CryotoContext"


ReactDOM.render(
  <>
    <>
      <BrowserRouter>
      <CryptoContext>
        <App3 />
        </CryptoContext>
      </BrowserRouter>
    </>
  </>, document.getElementById('root')
)
